    dc:creator "Tanasevitch, Andrei V." ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "On linyphiid spiders from Java, Indonesia, with the description of three new genera and four new species (Araneae: Linyphiidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5743523>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5743531> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5743523>
    dc:description "Figs 1-9. Photographs of males: the holotype of Javagone maribaya sp. nov. (1-4), the paratype of Javanaria gracilipes sp. nov. (5-6) and the holotype (7) and both paratypes (8-9) of Javanyphia gede sp. nov. (1, 5, 8-9) Habitus, dorsal view. (2, 6-7) Prosoma, lateral view. (3) Prosoma, frontal view. (4). Prosoma, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5743523/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5743531>
    dc:description "Figs 21-25. Details of male palp structure of Javanyphia gede sp. nov., paratype. (21-22) Right palp, retrolateral and prolateral views, respectively. (23) Palpal tibia, dorsal view.(24) Paracymbium, lateral view. (25) Distal suprategular apophysis and embolic division, ventro-lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5743531/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

